text: Ance Féas is a commune of the Pyrénées-Atlantiques département in the southwestern part of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Féas (the seat) and Ance.Arrêté préfectoral 19 July 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Ance Feas
title: Ance Féas
